#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.104"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.104:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.104:0.2"
msgid "11. Sambodhavagga "
msgstr "11. Awakening "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.104:0.3"
msgid "104. Paṭhamaassādasutta "
msgstr "104. Gratification (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an3.104:1.1"
msgid "“Lokassāhaṃ, bhikkhave, assādapariyesanaṃ acariṃ. Yo loke assādo tadajjhagamaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I went in search of the world’s gratification, and I found it. "

msgctxt "an3.104:1.2"
msgid "Yāvatako loke assādo, paññāya me so sudiṭṭho. "
msgstr "I’ve seen clearly with wisdom the full extent of gratification in the world. "

msgctxt "an3.104:1.3"
msgid "Lokassāhaṃ, bhikkhave, ādīnavapariyesanaṃ acariṃ. Yo loke ādīnavo tadajjhagamaṃ. "
msgstr "I went in search of the world’s drawbacks, and I found them. "

msgctxt "an3.104:1.4"
msgid "Yāvatako loke ādīnavo, paññāya me so sudiṭṭho. "
msgstr "I’ve seen clearly with wisdom the full extent of the drawbacks in the world. "

msgctxt "an3.104:1.5"
msgid "Lokassāhaṃ, bhikkhave, nissaraṇapariyesanaṃ acariṃ. Yaṃ loke nissaraṇaṃ tadajjhagamaṃ. "
msgstr "I went in search of escape from the world, and I found it. "

msgctxt "an3.104:1.6"
msgid "Yāvatakaṃ loke nissaraṇaṃ, paññāya me taṃ sudiṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr "I’ve seen clearly with wisdom the full extent of escape from the world. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.104:1.7"
msgid "Yāvakīvañcāhaṃ, bhikkhave, lokassa assādañca assādato ādīnavañca ādīnavato nissaraṇañca nissaraṇato yathābhūtaṃ nābbhaññāsiṃ, neva tāvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya ‘anuttaraṃ sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddho’ti paccaññāsiṃ. "
msgstr "As long as I didn’t truly understand the world’s gratification, drawback, and escape for what they are, I didn’t announce my supreme perfect awakening in this world with its gods, Māras, and Brahmās, this population with its ascetics and brahmins, its gods and humans. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.104:1.8"
msgid "Yato ca khvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, lokassa assādañca assādato ādīnavañca ādīnavato nissaraṇañca nissaraṇato yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ, athāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya ‘anuttaraṃ sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddho’ti paccaññāsiṃ. "
msgstr "But when I did truly understand the world’s gratification, drawback, and escape for what they are, I announced my supreme perfect awakening in this world with its gods, Māras, and Brahmās, this population with its ascetics and brahmins, its gods and humans. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.104:1.9"
msgid "Ñāṇañca pana me dassanaṃ udapādi: "
msgstr "Knowledge and vision arose in me: "

msgctxt "an3.104:1.10"
msgid "‘akuppā me vimutti, ayamantimā jāti, natthi dāni punabbhavo’”ti. "
msgstr "‘My freedom is unshakable; this is my last rebirth; now there are no more future lives.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.104:1.11"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

